{
  "id": "69c0a0fcd1d87338f12a8c1c",
  "title": "人類の人口",
  "created": 1774231812,
  "updated": 1774234464,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c0a0fcd1d87338f12a8c1c",
      "text": "人類の人口",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231812,
      "updated": 1774231812
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1fb0000000000991ec6",
      "text": "\tデビルマン 40億人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774232059,
      "updated": 1774232088
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a2090000000000991ec7",
      "text": "\t[アルマゲドン] 60億人",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774232074,
      "updated": 1774234464
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1e20000000000991ec3",
      "text": "\t[オデッセイ] 70億人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774232035,
      "updated": 1774232044
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1eb0000000000991ec4",
      "text": "\tヘイルメアリー 80億人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774232043,
      "updated": 1774232054
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1f50000000000991ec5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774232054,
      "updated": 1774232055
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1030000000000991eae",
      "text": ">[campintheair https://x.com/campintheair/status/2035538058075062685] なんか10億人増えてるぞ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231812,
      "updated": 1774231818
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1090000000000991eaf",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HD-u8_da4AArzFq?format=jpg&name=900x900#.png] [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HD-u9yCbYAANWtQ?format=jpg&name=900x900#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231818,
      "updated": 1774231818
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1090000000000991eb0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231818,
      "updated": 1774231821
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1090000000000991eb5",
      "text": ">[campintheair https://x.com/campintheair/status/2035606080630423580] 人類は結構なスピードで増えてるんだね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231818,
      "updated": 1774231818
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1090000000000991eb6",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HD_s8QOboAAK-bU?format=jpg&name=small#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231818,
      "updated": 1774231818
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1090000000000991eb7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231818,
      "updated": 1774231852
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1280000000000991ebb",
      "text": ">[TsukiyaNoi https://x.com/TsukiyaNoi/status/2035709809195131068] はじめまして",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231848,
      "updated": 1774231848
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1280000000000991ebc",
      "text": "> ウルトラセブン放送時の60年代後半は30億人でしたから、約半世紀で50億くらい増えてますよね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231848,
      "updated": 1774231848
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1280000000000991ebd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231848,
      "updated": 1774231867
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1370000000000991ec1",
      "text": ">[ohuyusann https://x.com/ohuyusann/status/2035622853027246106] デビルマン読んだら「世界には40億人の人口がいます」で吐きそうになるぞ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231864,
      "updated": 1774231864
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a1370000000000991ec2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774231864,
      "updated": 1774231864
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a55d00000000008d04f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232926,
      "updated": 1774232926
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a52000000000008d04f1",
      "text": "[sta.icon]理解した",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232866,
      "updated": 1774232879
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a52000000000008d04f3",
      "text": "\t作品ごとの世界人口の設定がテキトーすぎというわけではなく、その作品の時代当時の人口が反映されてる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232866,
      "updated": 1774232947
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a53b00000000008d04f4",
      "text": "\t\tデビルマンは1970年代、このときは世界人口は40億人くらい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232892,
      "updated": 1774232907
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a54a00000000008d04f5",
      "text": "\t\tヘイルメアリーは2021年、このとき世界人口は78億くらいで≒80人",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232907,
      "updated": 1774232923
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a52000000000008d04f2",
      "text": "\tつか今80億もいるのか、知らなかった",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232866,
      "updated": 1774232987
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a59900000000008d04f8",
      "text": "\t\t60億人くらいのイメージだった",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232987,
      "updated": 1774232995
    },
    {
      "id": "69c0a59300000000008d04f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774232980,
      "updated": 1774232980
    }
  ]
}